##creating storage 
step_1: open azure and go to storage services.
step_2: give basic configurations and check network encryption public
step_3: click on review+create
step_4: after successful creation of storage go to static web.
step_5: click on enable and enter name for web index and return path
step_6: now go to containers and click on web.
step_7: now upload a file.
step_8: now again go back to static web and copy web link
step_9: now open the link in a browser and u can access the file
